00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:08,339
Elisabeth Kübler-Ross, a Swiss psychologist who devoted her life to patients on the brink of death, once said:

2
00:00:08,699 --> 00:00:19,000
"The most beautiful people I have known are those who have known defeat, suffering, struggle, and loss, and have found their way out of the depths.

3
00:00:19,899 --> 00:00:30,899
